{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1703-02_5","head":{"value":"[Madrigal à « Louis le Grand » de M. l’abbé de Poissy]*","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", février 1703 [tome 2], p. 5-6.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"On réussit toujours bien lorsque l’on travaille sur une belle matiere, quand mesme on n’auroit pas un genie aussi heureux que M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" l’Abbé de Poissi qui a fait le Madrigal que vous allez lire.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"label":{"value":"À LOUIS LE GRAND.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puissant &amp; sage Politique,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il faut sur ton Sujet qu’en deux mots je m’explique.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Prince, de grace écoute moy,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La matiere en vaut bien la peine.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si l’Univers admire en toy","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le grand Soldat &amp; le grand Capitaine.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il y rencontre un plus grand Roy.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}}]}}}}